00:20:19.420 --> 00:20:21.020
Pagkatapos, kailangan mong pakasalan ako.

00:20:21.940 --> 00:20:23.300
Gu Chusheng, napakasama mo.

00:20:31.460 --> 00:20:32.300
Chu Yu,

00:20:32.300 --> 00:20:33.300
