00:25:19.260 --> 00:25:20.100
sa loob at labas

00:25:20.460 --> 00:25:21.300
ang hukuman.

00:25:21.820 --> 00:25:23.260
Gagawa ako ng mapayapang mundo

00:25:23.940 --> 00:25:25.340
